{
  "stem": "9091.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe we could pass and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] waiting for a chance to pass to  the other side.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll tell you truthfully, it was very bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know it wasn't much what to eat, because it was a closed field, a huge field, and there was nothing around it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I don't know what really we used to-- I think there were some stuff that my grandmother that lived with us cooked and prepared [INAUDIBLE] and some bread and what that we had with us.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I guess that's what we ate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There is one episode, actually, that I remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I always remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] [DRINKS] We were coming close to the border, and there was-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] there was a fence there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And beyond the fence, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] you couldn't pass, only if you passed a certain gate.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At that gate was standing Gestapo, SS men, and a Pole.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The Germans actually couldn't [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] tell a difference between a Jew and a Pole, unless he was bearded with, you know, a typical Jewish person, like all traditional.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But other than that, they couldn't really tell a difference.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The ones that guided them were the Poles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was six years old, and I still remember it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I came to the gate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was that Gestapo and the Pole standing there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the Pole would point out-- Pole, Jew, Pole, Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the Jews, they were sent aside, couldn't pass the gate, and they let the Poles pass.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Somehow, I guess, we found an opening somewhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We went along the fence there for quite some while, and we looked and looked and looked.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
